---
title: Tuscan Chicken Linguine with Roasted Tomato, Basil, and a Creamy Parmesan Sauce
description: Our chefs just took pasta night to the next level: thanks to linguine, tomatoes, and chicken with Tuscan herbs, this recipe has all the Italian flair you could want and then some. The dish is accompanied by a sauce that has all the creamy goodness you want—it has cream cheese, Parmesan, and garlic herb butter for a trifecta of dairy deliciousness. So get ready: these tasty noodles are waiting to get twirled ‘round your fork.
